{"tid":2219663,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迪姆華拿曾因一場波質疑車路士　「完成拼圖」可比歐聯冠軍","createTime":"2020-09-27T04:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T07:55:05.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8dba8ec590b384d452bb8791e8b086ec6a74e23e","tid":2219663,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T04:50:58.000Z","msg":"德國前鋒迪姆華拿（Timo Werner）今夏由RB萊比鍚，轉投英超的車路士。這名「德意志射手」早前承認，看過拜仁慕尼黑去季歐聯16強大炒新東家的比賽後，一度「懷疑人生」。<br />\n<br />\n車路士去季歐聯16強遇上拜仁慕尼黑，2月舉行的首回合遭德甲班霸大炒3：0。華拿最近接受德國《圖片報》訪問，直認那一場比賽曾使自己懷疑應否移居倫敦。<br />\n<br />\n「如果我說車路士歐聯主場遭拜仁大炒3：0一戰，沒有影響決定應否轉投車路士的話，我絕對是個騙子。」華拿說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這名24歲當時仍效力舊東家RB萊比鍚，在德甲一直都緊咬拜仁，每次對賽戰情緊湊，聯賽步步進逼。如此看來，當時的車路士實力，比不上近年於德甲冒起的萊比錫。<br />\n<br />\n不過，「藍戰士」今夏大肆擴軍，除華拿以4800萬英鎊「上車」外，又收購了6名球員，更即將簽得雷恩門將艾度亞文迪（Edouard Mendy）。華拿認為車路士戰力急升，可於歐洲賽大展拳腳。<br />\n<br />\n「拜仁暴露了車路士的弱點，車路士回應了」，華拿說：「他們完成了拼圖，實力已追上了拜仁慕尼黑。」<br />\n<br />\n華拿效力RB萊比錫4年，於各項比賽上陣159場攻入95球，暫時於英超仍未開齋。英超首戰助球隊以3：1擊敗白禮頓後，怹有感英超的風格及節奏大相逕庭，直言「與德甲比有如兩個世界」。"},{"pid":"b577c667bd9f0bc5ce152417a03b1c283b204490","tid":2219663,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:04:15.000Z","msg":"睇左兩場，車個問題會唔會係林伯到"},{"pid":"63caaa15c3d7b1c665c5a0a3f6c11a8c8a11c11d","tid":2219663,"uid":92172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b577c667bd9f0bc5ce152417a03b1c283b204490","tid":2219663,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:04:15.000Z","msg":"睇左兩場，車個問題會唔會係林伯到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"叫撚伯落場踢"},{"pid":"5d6e3104a8d33f516a87ac50d24e18db38606391","tid":2219663,"uid":60524,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:40:02.000Z","msg":"人又買得多過人<br />\n對白禮頓失3球 仲要補時逼和<br />\n個濕鳩名宿領隊自己切腹啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8bbfef979259afc3ffb4fa03b82d7b5fdb8d82","tid":2219663,"uid":60524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:41:58.000Z","msg":"西布朗先真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e7e76fcead0a44fe1ceb9e6aa138bf1814e190","tid":2219663,"uid":129862,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:50:58.000Z","msg":"其實佢自己都哂左唔少機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7344f786986b5547b482fff2495b63e56941d913","tid":2219663,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T05:57:58.000Z","msg":"希望佢唔好變莫拉達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5fe4f3976369f4b20b3209fe50d2eaae7e4991","tid":2219663,"uid":7585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:25:13.000Z","msg":"呢3場佢自己都成陣女人達味啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f3a0f6eb7fae38413283f70e0c871a3de8fa55","tid":2219663,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"水貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800b96a5b759d0c20b55380f109b7fc036114aac","tid":2219663,"uid":48161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:26:49.000Z","msg":"去拜仁咪無事囉"},{"pid":"0228306c1169088a1dfaab53e05f93070273ec42","tid":2219663,"uid":15211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:27:33.000Z","msg":"又拼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da676d27463f03a0e5c8fde088c9789c3375f82a","tid":2219663,"uid":89538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T06:29:14.000Z","msg":"車仔 前鋒墳墓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s